                                                    <CheckBox text="1 Air" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                    <CheckBox text="2 Drum" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                    <CheckBox text="3 Damper" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                    <CheckBox text="4 Burner" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                    <CheckBox text="5 —" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                </HBox>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Buttons">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <HBox spacing="16">
                                                <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="secondary-section-card settings-card-emphasis" HBox.hgrow="ALWAYS">
                                                    <Label text="Event Buttons" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Настройка кастомных кнопок и поведения панели управления под графиком." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                                    <Button fx:id="btnEventButtons" text="Открыть Event Buttons…" styleClass="btn-secondary"/>
                                                </VBox>
                                                <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="secondary-section-card" HBox.hgrow="ALWAYS">
                                                    <Label text="Команды Modbus" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="write(slaveId,reg,val); wcoil(slaveId,coil,0|1); sleep(sec). Запускаются для основных событий обжара." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                                </VBox>
                                            </HBox>
                                            <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Привязка команд к событиям (Default Buttons)" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <GridPane styleClass="secondary-grid" hgap="12" vgap="8">
                                                    <columnConstraints>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="120" prefWidth="140"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints hgrow="ALWAYS"/>
                                                    </columnConstraints>
                                                    <Label text="CHARGE" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtEventCharge" promptText="write(1,1008,2);sleep(15)" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="0"/>
                                                    <Label text="DROP" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="1" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtEventDrop" promptText="write(1,1008,5)" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <Label text="DRY_END (DE)" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="2" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtEventDryEnd" promptText="wcoil(1,2005,1)" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <Label text="FC_START" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="3" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtEventFcStart" promptText="write(1,1008,3)" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <Label text="COOL_END" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="4" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtEventCoolEnd" promptText="write(1,1008,0)" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                </GridPane>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Sliders">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <Label text="Sliders — привязка событий Air, Drum, Damper, Burner к командам (Action, Command, Min, Max, Factor, Offset). По образцу Artisan Events → Sliders." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Таблица слайдеров" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <Label text="Здесь будет таблица: Event, Action, Command, Min, Max, Factor, Offset, Bernoulli, Step, Temp Unit. Содержимое — в следующих итерациях." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Quantifiers">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Квантайзеры событий" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <Label text="Для слайдеров Air, Drum, Damper и Burner: source, SV, min, max, step и action. Значения применяются при сохранении." wrapText="true" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                                <GridPane fx:id="quantifiersGrid" styleClass="secondary-grid" hgap="12" vgap="8">
                                                    <columnConstraints>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="90" prefWidth="110"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="90" prefWidth="100"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="55" prefWidth="65"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="55" prefWidth="65"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="55" prefWidth="65"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="55" prefWidth="65"/>
                                                        <ColumnConstraints minWidth="65" prefWidth="75"/>
                                                    </columnConstraints>
                                                    <Label text="Событие" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Source" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="SV" GridPane.columnIndex="2" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Min" GridPane.columnIndex="3" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Max" GridPane.columnIndex="4" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Step" GridPane.columnIndex="5" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                    <Label text="Action" GridPane.columnIndex="6" GridPane.rowIndex="0" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>

                                                    <Label text="Air" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="1" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <ComboBox fx:id="cmbQuantAirSource" prefWidth="90" styleClass="secondary-combo" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantAirSv" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="2" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantAirMin" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="3" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantAirMax" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="4" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantAirStep" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="5" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>
                                                    <CheckBox fx:id="chkQuantAirAction" GridPane.columnIndex="6" GridPane.rowIndex="1"/>

                                                    <Label text="Drum" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="2" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <ComboBox fx:id="cmbQuantDrumSource" prefWidth="90" styleClass="secondary-combo" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDrumSv" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="2" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDrumMin" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="3" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDrumMax" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="4" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDrumStep" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="5" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>
                                                    <CheckBox fx:id="chkQuantDrumAction" GridPane.columnIndex="6" GridPane.rowIndex="2"/>

                                                    <Label text="Damper" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="3" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <ComboBox fx:id="cmbQuantDamperSource" prefWidth="90" styleClass="secondary-combo" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDamperSv" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="2" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDamperMin" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="3" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDamperMax" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="4" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantDamperStep" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="5" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>
                                                    <CheckBox fx:id="chkQuantDamperAction" GridPane.columnIndex="6" GridPane.rowIndex="3"/>

                                                    <Label text="Burner" GridPane.columnIndex="0" GridPane.rowIndex="4" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <ComboBox fx:id="cmbQuantBurnerSource" prefWidth="90" styleClass="secondary-combo" GridPane.columnIndex="1" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantBurnerSv" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="2" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantBurnerMin" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="3" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantBurnerMax" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="4" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                    <TextField fx:id="txtQuantBurnerStep" prefWidth="55" styleClass="secondary-input" GridPane.columnIndex="5" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                    <CheckBox fx:id="chkQuantBurnerAction" GridPane.columnIndex="6" GridPane.rowIndex="4"/>
                                                </GridPane>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Palettes">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <Label text="Palettes — управление палитрами кнопок (Store Palette, Activate Palette). По образцу Artisan Events → Palettes." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Management" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <HBox spacing="10" alignment="CENTER_LEFT">
                                                    <Button text="&lt;&lt; Store Palette" styleClass="btn-secondary"/>
                                                    <Label text="current:" styleClass="secondary-field-label"/>
                                                    <TextField promptText="default" prefWidth="120" styleClass="secondary-input"/>
                                                    <Button text="Activate Palette &gt;&gt;" styleClass="btn-secondary"/>
                                                </HBox>
                                                <CheckBox text="Switch Using Number Keys + Cmd" styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Style">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <Label text="Style — цвет, текст, маркер, толщина, прозрачность, размер для типов событий (Air, Drum, Damper, Burner). По образцу Artisan Events → Style." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Стили событий" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <Label text="Таблица: Color, Text Color, Marker, Thickness, Opacity, Size. Содержимое — в следующих итерациях." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                                <Tab text="Annotations">
                                    <content>
                                        <VBox spacing="12" styleClass="settings-content-column">
                                            <Label text="Annotations — шаблоны подписей к событиям на графике (Show, Annotation, Example before/after FCs). По образцу Artisan Events → Annotations." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            <VBox spacing="10" styleClass="secondary-section-card">
                                                <Label text="Annotation" styleClass="secondary-section-title"/>
                                                <Label text="Поля Show и Annotation для типов Air, Drum, Damper, Burner; Allowed Annotation Overlap. Содержимое — в следующих итерациях." styleClass="secondary-hint-label" wrapText="true"/>
                                            </VBox>
                                        </VBox>
                                    </content>
                                </Tab>
                            </tabs>
                        </TabPane>
                    </VBox>
                </ScrollPane>
            </VBox>
        </VBox>
    </HBox>

    <HBox spacing="12" alignment="CENTER_LEFT" styleClass="secondary-action-row settings-bottom-bar">
        <Label text="Изменения применяются после сохранения. Визуальные настройки можно preview в реальном времени." styleClass="secondary-hint-label"/>
        <Region HBox.hgrow="ALWAYS"/>
        <Button fx:id="btnCancel" text="Отмена" styleClass="btn-secondary"/>
        <Button fx:id="btnSave" text="Сохранить" styleClass="btn-primary"/>
    </HBox>
</VBox>
